'''Facha'''
Generally refers to clothing in poor condition because of overuse. It can also mean clothing in good condition, but it's too informal for a specific occasion.
Ex: Wearing a T-shirt, shorts and flip-slops to the office.

Similar terms: Fachoso (masculine), Fachosa (femeinine). Refers to a person who dresses very informally very often.

